Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.03,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You were late today, Ebata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.86,Default,Ebata,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's fine. But I must ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.53,Default,Ebata,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.04,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Whatever makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.79,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,960)}Yes, all five are working hard.
Comment: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.21,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.21,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.00,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then I expect good things from their finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.30,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,May I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I have a bit of a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.05,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:33.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd like to quit tutoring as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:38.89,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you aware that Nino and Itsuki\Ngot in a fight and ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.23,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I never heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:43.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Have they resolved their issues?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.32,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:45.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:46.44,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:47.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.53,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Aren't you curious about \Nwhy they got in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:56.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't you care to know what they're thinking or what's bothering them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I shouldn't talk like that to my employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:03.21,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.21,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why don't you try acting \Nlike a father like once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.38,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}... You've gone and done it now.
Comment: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.97,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,960)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.25,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.31,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I won't give my daughters to a man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.95,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.91,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd always gotten allowances until last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.46,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I should have stayed home to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.63,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,"Good fortune"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.17,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.42,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.55,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I don't need my fortune told\Nto know how my year's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.93,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ever since I met those girls,\NI've always had...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.56,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,the worst luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.82,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san} and Raiha{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} always around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.82,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop by our place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Nah, we'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.82,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.66,Italics,TV,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.83,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,They kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why did you even invite us over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:56.09,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Come on, it's the new year. Let's relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.72,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.27,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I made a New Year's meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.14,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.65,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Raiha{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.73,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.86,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I think I had the wrong idea about you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.78,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'd heard your family was really rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.20,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,O-Oh, well, things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.58,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry we don't really have much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.25,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We have to return the kimonos \Nto our landlord, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.76,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Anyway, you can make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.63,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.63,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you guys sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.51,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.67,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why are you sitting over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.26,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Isn't it cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.51,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Get in the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay, Raiha, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.52,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.90,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'll give you a massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.23,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.15,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No, I'm not really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.86,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,No fair, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.41,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,First come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.62,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I get his arms, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.20,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.41,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'd like to massage his legs, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.42,Italics,Raiha,0,0,0,,Brother{*Onii-chan}'s popular all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:16.25,Italics,Raiha,0,0,0,,Mom, spring has come early for Big Brother{*Onii-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.51,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are you guys plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.17,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Urp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.60,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.64,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,We're just thanking you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.68,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.60,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You always work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.93,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Something's really fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.11,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Please have some of my food, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.44,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Way too fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.86,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's play the face matching game\N to get into the party mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.16,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We made a quintuplets version!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.57,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That's way too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.79,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There's something we'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.58,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's too early for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.20,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go to the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.71,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are they scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.84,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it bothers him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.59,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:05.60,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We're asking him to continue \Nteaching us without pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.56,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want to do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.94,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,And I don't want to depend on Father,\N if we can avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:17.44,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But what is there that we could do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Th-That's inappropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.20,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You were thinking the same thing,\N weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.62,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that'd make Futaro{**-kun} happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Who knows? He's a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.75,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're an actress, aren't you? \NYou could give him a peck on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.96,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Wh-What exactly do you think actresses do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.51,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,B-But I mean, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What about you, Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.51,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And Futaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.64,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.22,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.77,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You've really led me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can't stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.86,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,N-No, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.32,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.36,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Wait, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.28,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.49,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.50,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why not just do something \Nnormal and cook for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You're good at cooking, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Make him some snacks or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.34,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I was finally getting over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:27.13,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we just go tell him\Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:28.93,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.81,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.35,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,1960,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.18,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Comment: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.10,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,200,\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(560,720,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&))}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.10,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,This is Ichika's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.44,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.15,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.78,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You guys are playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.57,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,We changed the rules, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.66,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.00,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, you have cream on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.67,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,B-Brother{*O-Onii-chan}! Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.76,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's just call that peck on the cheek\Na payment for your tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.39,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that from Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.80,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,She caught me off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.43,Italics,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.31,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:22.82,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We aren't in any position to \Ncompensate you fairly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, you could have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm just doing it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't worry about paying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.58,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can just give me a cut \Nwhen you make it big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:40.71,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I want it in writing! Five thousand yen\Nper person per day of tutoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.75,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And I {\i1}will{\i0} collect, right down to the last yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.59,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Right, that's how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.26,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And all five of you are here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's get cracking on the winter homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Winter homework, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.47,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.10,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:01.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We've all done our homework already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well, let's just make it a \Nregular study session, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:07.99,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Big Brother{*Onii-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.49,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'm going to go home\Nso I don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.37,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.66,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Can you help me with this bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.80,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,"Provide examples of words ending with -ish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.67,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,-ish is a suffix that means "approximately,"\Nor kind of. So you have "pinkish"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:34.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,"Bookish," "thickish"...\NThere's also peckish, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.56,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:38.85,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.18,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.60,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichika, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.94,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm not... sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.03,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.53,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Let her sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:57.54,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika's been working even more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.70,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,She is paying our bills and expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:05.38,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Ichika\N that we get to have you here to teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:09.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But what's the point\Nif she can't focus on studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.51,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey, wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.17,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.93,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why don't we work, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.60,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Do you have any work experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.18,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I-I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Will you have time to both study and work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All of you are struggling to even pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.44,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll work as a tutor, like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.78,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll teach as I study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.20,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That way, I can improve \Nmy academics, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.78,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd feel sorry for your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:45.25,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,How about working at a supermarket, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.21,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You'd be fired instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.34,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want to try working at a maid café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.84,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You might be surprisingly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.09,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Permission denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:54.43,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You'd probably be \Na dominatrix, right, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.68,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Nino would work in food service, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,If I had to choose, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's always been your dream \Nto open your own shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's just a silly idea I had as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Don't take it too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.36,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I know a good cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Mille-feuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Eclairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.33,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Mont Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.99,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.25,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I've worked several jobs so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all took some commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.13,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Now's the time to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:47.39,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Ichika! Please stop\N taking your clothes off in your sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.94,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Look away! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.27,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:57.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I underestimated this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:10.54,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.16,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.05,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.81,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well? What do you think of my pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's just like yours, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.43,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Give me a raise, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.81,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's underdone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be talking trash about Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:36.32,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be a while\N before I can let you in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.07,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.32,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}, you can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.58,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.58,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We're closing at noon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.96,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We're renting the shop out\Nfor a movie shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You could have told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.96,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.38,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Looking forward to working with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.38,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,If the movie takes off,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the fans will be coming in \Ndroves to visit the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:10.35,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We'll have a pick with our business name\Nin the cakes that will be on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.86,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I wish I had his insatiable hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.19,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,That looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.45,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:19.11,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:27.12,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.33,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Scene 37-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.38,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:39.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to try this cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:43.01,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Now's not the time, Tamako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.80,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.89,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,That's the cursed reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.02,Default,Person C,0,0,0,,They say if you get one, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:55.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm too dumb to know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:59.53,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Let's just have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.33,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What, Tamako{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.79,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,would you mind not watching? \NIt's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.75,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why would you take up embarrassing work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.09,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm trying not to tell the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're running out of savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:24.10,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I mean, it turns out food and power\Nis a lot more expensive than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.81,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,So I decided to accept any work I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:31.31,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I have to be strong for the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.35,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,So don't try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.84,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm not going to dismiss your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:41.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And I'm grateful to you for giving me\Nan opportunity to continue tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:45.36,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you could do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:49.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Isn't this job still pretty unprofitable\Nfor how much it ties you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.33,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Miss Nakano{*Nakano-san}, we're ready to start rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.04,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.97,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.26,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.76,Default,Director,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.68,Default,Director,0,0,0,,That one was good,\N but why don't we try another take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:09.85,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:14.35,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I wish the others could see her\Nbeing so ditzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:18.36,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind us using \Nthis pie for one more take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.36,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.49,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,The pick's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.74,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's the dud that I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.99,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Ready! Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.00,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Nice! That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.14,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You got Problem 5 wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.93,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.14,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.90,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,These things are only cool\Nwhen done in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.94,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you done with your script?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.65,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.36,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I memorized the whole thing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why can't you use that skill for studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.87,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,The curse kills me in the first part,\Nso I don't have that many lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.91,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You die a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.00,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.79,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Is the cake here all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,If I'm being kind, it was unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.63,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,If I'm being brutal,\N it was like Miku's home cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.18,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But you saved my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was an impressive lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.31,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,It's called {\i1}acting{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.44,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's true that you surprised me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I mean, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Y-You're kind of growing into \Nyour job as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.32,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.32,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She almost had me saying \Nsomething smug to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:57.91,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Man, I'm amazed you can hide your\Nembarrassment in front of so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:01.08,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I really wish the others could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Good work, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.34,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I hate that I'm even acting\Nin this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.60,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Now I really am lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:20.39,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But I couldn't let him see my face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.36,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.53,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Stay calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:32.91,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Remember your mechanics!\N The most efficient way of carrying this load is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.62,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hurry up, you bag handlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why'd you call me out at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,They're having a sale today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.34,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,And you should be able\Nto carry that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.88,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} carry it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.64,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku asked me to buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She's eating all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.64,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're pretty dense for \Nsomeone who's so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.52,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's so early, too. It's only January.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.40,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.23,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Wait, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.03,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Can you hold this for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.29,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.16,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.37,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.42,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Something's weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:35.68,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't gotten over Kintaro{**-kun} yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.93,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.68,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.31,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:46.44,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,There's no way this guy's my prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.44,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Nino, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.24,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Bring us every kind of sandwich you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:00.83,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.33,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.62,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You don't want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.34,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll take them. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.46,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.55,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're amenable and quick \Nto understand, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:18.22,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I believe that's what is meant\Nwhen one is called "intelligent."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I knew it. It's Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Why is he with Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.23,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was definitely him.
Comment: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.94,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\t(2920,3200,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}That was him at the hospital back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.69,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was him at the hospital back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.49,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That man is their father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Now, Itsuki{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:39.40,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll turn a blind eye to the mistake\Nyou girls have made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.79,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Come back home with the others immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.62,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Inform all of your sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Does that include him as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.00,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You mean Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.59,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is a family matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.72,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He's an outsider in every sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.72,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.77,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That's so childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.19,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What did you do to Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I-I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,G-Gee, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.02,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We can't go home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:17.90,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,He's far too involved in this\Nto call him an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.28,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then how about this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll allow Uesugi{**-kun} back into the home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask him to continue tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.79,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But he'll be working alongside \Na professional tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.55,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He'll be acting as her support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.17,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But we're all working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:41.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Do you even suppose, if Uesugi{**-kun} was \Nbrought back in as your tutor as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that Yotsuba{**-kun} could earn a passing grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:53.82,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,From what I've seen of her grades in\Nthe second term, I have very little hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:56.57,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.16,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You'll only make things worse if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.95,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We'll have a better chance with two tutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.83,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.04,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:17.09,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san} and the five of us can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.01,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I want the six of us to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.09,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So please, believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.97,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We won't make the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.10,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And if you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.06,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I would rather not say this out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've made an arrangement \Nwith an acquaintance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,who is a board member at a high school that\Nwould allow you to enroll as third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,If you fail on the next exam, \NI'll have you transfer to that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:48.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,If you insist on doing things your way,\Nthe responsibility is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.21,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:58.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I knew you would, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll finalize the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:01.51,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:05.30,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We'll accept the condition that we \Ntransfer schools if we don't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:11.69,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm not an amenable, \Nunderstanding, intelligent child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:18.32,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It seems that the duty of a parent is to \Nhear the selfish demands of their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:22.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And it's also the duty of a parent \Nto scold their selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:24.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:03.51,Default,Text,0,0,0,,"The Last Exam."
